snippet.textDisplay:
HORROR   Revelation 8:11-13
I find myself staying away from horror movies over the past few years, it’s not that I am scared but the gore/demonism/violence/evil content; can stay with you for a while and taint your perspective of the world and life in general (for a few hours to a few days). As I read revelation where JESUS breaks the seven seals and imagine the reaction of those left behind on earth as the fabric of their world is torn apart a third at a time, I realized this is real horror! Forget ghost and gore; when all you relied on, took for granted, and though was safe; falls apart, leaving you exposed, you will be afraid. Let JESUS take you away from all this.
